nodes.text: A male who was the brother of Five World Deputy Prime Minister Denjax Teppler served the Corellian Security Force in 40 ABY. He programmed four YVH-Series battle droids to be loyal to Teppler during tensions between Corellia and the Galactic Federation of Free Alliances, and later served as a bodyguard to Five World Prime Minister Aidel Saxan when she met with Galactic Alliance representatives on Toryaz Station. Both he and Saxan were killed there.
